Description: Al Omran Industrial Trading Co (known as: Al Omran) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Parallel Market” (NOMU) since February 2017. Al Omran operates within the Consumer Durables & Apparel sector focusing on Consumer Electronics. Al Omran is based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia and was established in June 2003.
